Name: Aragorn
Text: Celestina my love, I HAVE DONE IT!

Name: Aragorn
Text: I-It's...going to be okay my beloved. You'll be full of life and in my arms soon enough.

Name: Aragorn
Text: Astrea, my goddess! My devotion for you knows no bounds I owe my life to you! My dear Celee will be well than-

Name: Astrea
Text: Aragorn you blind slighted knight. What an unexpected turn this has taken.

Name: Astrea
Text: You never were exceptional so I never assumed you would make it here. That miserable Scholar alone should have been enought to kill you.

Name: Astrea
Text: It was fun watching your struggle but you have long overstayed your welcome.

Name: Aragorn
Text: Goddess, what are you saying? I made it the divine water! You said my beloved would be saved if I obtained it!

Name: Aragorn
Text: NO! This is a trick! WHO ARE YOU! Where is Goddess Astrea! OUR GRACIOUS GODDESS WOULD NEVER-

Name: Astrea
Text: Hahaha. You speak as if your words matter. All that faith for a lie. Faith was all that you had and your should have known that wasn't enough.

Name: Astrea
Text: Your whining is getting annoying. Why not give me a moment's entertainment before your death.
